Package edu.harvard.util.graph.summarizer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BaseSummaryChecker
    Interface for determining which nodes can be grouped
    BaseSummaryLabeler
    Interface for determining how to label summary nodes
    GraphSummarizer
    A group builder
    ObservableGraphSummarizer
    A group builder
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseSummaryCheckers
    A collection of miscellaneous summary checkers
    BaseSummaryCheckers.ConsecutiveIndex
    Summary checker for nodes with the same (index / some constant).
    BaseSummaryCheckers.Hash
    Summary checker for nodes with the same (index % some constant).
    BaseSummaryCheckers.RegEx
    Summary checker for nodes satisfying the same regex
    BaseSummaryCheckers.SameConnectedNodes
    Summary checker for nodes connected to the same nodes
    GenericGraphSummarizer
    A generic group builder: robust, but slow -- on the order of O(n^2) per pass
    SmallGroupsGraphSummarizer
    A simple graph summarizer that arbitrarily breaks large summaries into small groups
    SummarizerUtils
    Miscellaneous utility methods useful for graph summarizations
    UniqueInOutSummarizer
    Summarize using unique input/output relationships
